did.unittitle: Day book/ledger of lists of students, their college, and fees paid or tuition credits used, pp. 36-end (1874-1877)

scopecontent.head: Scope and Contents
scopecontent.p: Also includes a general ledger, pp. 1-35 (1874-1875, no index) with undated fund balances as well as lists of notes amounts and names.
